|archive-date=2008-09-13
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080913042934/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7588595.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>，10月12日主場3-1擊敗[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]交出一個漂亮助攻，鋒芒完全蓋過對手中場悍將[[沙維治|-{zh-hans:罗比·萨维奇; zh-hk:沙維治;}-]]<ref>{{en}} {{cite news
|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/football_league/article4926522.ece
|title=Fabian Delph leads Leeds charge
|date=2008-10-12
|accessdate=2008-11-22
|publisher=Times Online}}</ref>。其後於10月23日主場對[[沃尔索尔足球俱乐部|華素爾]]再轟入兩球遠程「世界波」，協助球隊輕勝3-0<ref>{{en}} {{cite news
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7674531.stm
|title=Leeds 3-0 Walsall
|date=2008-10-23
|accessdate=2008-11-22
|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport
|archive-date=2008-10-28
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081028024945/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/7674531.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。11月22日主場4-1擊敗[[哈特尔普尔联足球俱乐部|哈特普爾]]射入再度領前2-1的一球<ref>{{en}} {{cite news
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7727363.stm
