===阿士東維拉===
2009年8月4日，德爾夫加盟由[[馬田·奧尼爾|馬田·奧尼爾]]領軍的[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/8182303.stm |title=Aston Villa complete Delph deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-04 |accessdate=2009-08-05 |archive-date=2015-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150913144447/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/8182303.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年4月，德爾夫在操練時[[膝蓋|左膝]][[前十字韧带|前十字韧带]]撕裂，須要養傷長達8個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_6104145,00.html |title=Delph out for eight months |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2010-04-19 |accessdate=2012-01-21 |archive-date=2014-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331011108/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11677_6104145,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。德爾夫於[[节礼日|拆禮物日]]復出對[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:托特纳姆热刺; zh-hk:熱刺;}-]]後觸傷舊患再次缺陣2個月，於2011年2月26日，在主場4-1擊敗[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]後補入替再上戰場。3月3日，德爾夫與阿士東維拉續約四年留隊至2015年<ref name="contract extension">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/9413411.stm |title=Aston Villa's Fabian Delph signs contract extension |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-03 |accessdate=2012-01-21 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205174118/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/9413411.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====2011-12球季====
